hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: What's the last date I can post this to to arrive in time for Christmas? lornvillagepharmacy.com.au Johnny Weir is all about razzle-dazzle showmanship, but on New Year's Eve 2011, the Olympic skater threw a little bling into the mix. Weir, 27, tied the knot with boyfriend Victor Voronov to close out 2011, and tweeted his excitement to his nearly 103,000 Twitter followers. 'I'm married!' he wrote, later clarifying that the actual wedding will take place in the summer, though 'all the official stuff is done now! No more livin' in sin!'
